Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…到底在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 玲音
