Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实记忆…不只是过去的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它也关系到今天 甚至明天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就依照你刚才所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你的心意去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但睡房的窗帘由我决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的老师 你说什么就什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 这才是个好学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 请等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过你吗？ 有见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是我实习时教过的学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又不像 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是初次见面…的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？ 原来是初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.14,0:20:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是亚莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个普通的名字对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玲音 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定将来还会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 说不定会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远和你在一起 永远…
